title: Beat the Drum Slowly
description: A judge gathers up a "gang" to rob a casino with a reputation for cheating. His accomplices include two brothers who have been cheated there and a shady saloon girl. Things aren't quite what they seem, however, and the brothers are shocked when, as they're pulling off the heist, the judge suddenly pulls out a knife and stabs the casino owner to death.

title: The Cutups
description: A couple of grifters, posing as practical jokers, dupe Slim into holding up the Express Office. This results in Slim being thrown in jail, while the grifters divide the loot between themselves.

title: The Brathwaite Brothers
description: Three brothers want their money back from bank operators who have been robbed.
